data.description: Step into this impeccably maintained 3-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom Colonial home offering over 1,800 sq ft of comfortable living space. Located just minutes from downtown Fenton, this home invites you in with its warmth and charm. The updated kitchen boasts newer appliances, a central island, and wood floors. The open layout seamlessly connects the kitchen to the dining room and a cozy family room anchored by a beautiful fireplace, making it the perfect setting for gatherings and relaxation. Upstairs, you'll find three well-sized bedrooms, accompanied by a modern dual-sink bathroom that adds a touch of luxury and convenience to daily routines. Outside, a sprawling half-acre fenced yard awaits, complete with an expansive deck and a barn-style shed, offering ample space for outdoor enjoyment and storage. Recent updates include a new roof (2019), iron filter (2024), Generac generator with a new battery (2024), washer (2020), and dryer (2024). Don't miss the opportunity to call this home yours. Schedule your private showing today and experience the perfect blend of quality, comfort, and convenience!
